You have no plan deductible for orthodontics. Your lifetime individual benefit for orthodontics is $1250. To date you have used $300, so you have $950 still remaining.

By the way, as a valued customer you are eligible to apply for our Nurture Healthcare credit card with a maximum credit limit of $5,000.00. Would you like to apply now?
